            "body": "st seems too fast to even show the spinner with anything I throw at it. Can get it to show up properly with kitty, other terminals just seem to grind to a halt until the entire clipboard is pasted, showing a few throbs if luckyðŸ˜…\n\nThis does seem to make it work with ui2, but breaks some existing testsðŸ˜¢:\n```diff\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/message.c b/src/nvim/message.c\nindex 6e87a2990b..612b3653d5 100644\n--- a/src/nvim/message.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/message.c\n@@ -1675,6 +1675,7 @@ void msg_start(void)\n   }\n\n   if (!msg_scroll && full_screen) {     // overwrite last message\n+    msg_ext_overwrite = true;\n     msg_row = cmdline_row;\n     msg_col = 0;\n   } else if ((msg_didout || p_ch == 0) && !ui_has(kUIMessages)) {  // start message on next line\n```",
